## 4. 序列图 - API 调用完整流程

```plantuml
@startuml API 调用完整序列图

autonumber

participant "应用\n后端" as App #E8F5E9
participant "Token\n缓存" as Cache #F3E5F5
participant "飞书认证\n服务" as Auth #F3E5F5
participant "飞书 API\n网关" as Gateway #FFF3E0
participant "飞书业务\n服务" as Service #FFF3E0
participant "安全\n机制" as Security #ECEFF1

== Token 获取阶段 ==

App -> Cache: 检查缓存 token
activate Cache
Cache --> App: 无缓存或已过期
deactivate Cache

App -> Auth: POST /auth/v3/\ntenant_access_token/internal
activate Auth
note right: {"app_id","app_secret"}
Auth --> App: {"tenant_access_token","expire":7200}
deactivate Auth

App -> Cache: 缓存 token\n(提前 30 分钟刷新)
activate Cache
Cache --> App: OK
deactivate Cache

== API 调用阶段 ==

App -> Gateway: GET /contact/v3/users/{id}\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Security: 1. IP 白名单检查
activate Security
Security --> Gateway: IP 合法
deactivate Security

Gateway -> Security: 2. 凭证有效性验证
Security --> Gateway: token 有效
deactivate Security

Gateway -> Security: 3. 权限 Scope 检查
Security --> Gateway: 权限充足
deactivate Security

Gateway -> Service: 转发业务请求
activate Service
Service --> Gateway: 用户数据 JSON
deactivate Service

Gateway --> App: 200 OK + 数据
deactivate Gateway

== 错误处理 ==

group 常见错误处理
  App -> Gateway: 请求 API
  Gateway --> App: 99991664 (token 过期)
  App -> Auth: 刷新 token
  App -> Gateway: 重试请求
end

@enduml
```

