## 7. 状态图 - Token 生命周期

```plantuml
@startuml Token 生命周期状态图

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1976D2
  ArrowColor #37474F
}

[*] --> Requesting : 应用启动

state Requesting {
  [*] --> SendingRequest : 发起请求
  SendingRequest --> WaitingResponse : POST /auth/v3/...
  WaitingResponse --> Received : HTTP 200
  WaitingResponse --> Failed : HTTP 错误
}

state Received {
  [*] --> Active : token 生效
}

state Active {
  state Valid <<choice>> as V
  state NearExpiry <<choice>> as N
  
  Active --> V : 检查有效期
  Active --> N : 检查有效期
  
  V --> Active : expire > 30 分钟\n继续使用
  N --> Requesting : expire < 30 分钟\n刷新 token
}

state Expired {
  [*] --> Invalid : 超过 2 小时
  Invalid --> [*] : 清除缓存
}

state Failed {
  [*] --> Retryable : 可重试错误
  [*] --> Fatal : 致命错误
  
  Retryable --> Requesting : 重试
  Fatal --> [*] : 告警
}

Received --> Expired : 超时
Received --> Failed : 响应错误
Expired --> Requesting : 重新获取

note right of Active
  <b>有效期规则</b>
  - 最大：2 小时
  - 刷新点：30 分钟
  - 并发：最多 2 个
end note

note bottom of Failed
  <b>错误码</b>
  - 99991401: IP 白名单
  - 99991663: 无效凭证
  - 99991664: 凭证过期
  - 99991665: 权限不足
end note

@enduml
```

