## 附录：PlantUML 使用指南

### 在线渲染
- **官网**: https://plantuml.com/
- **在线编辑器**: https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml/

### VS Code 插件
1. 安装 `PlantUML` 插件 (作者：jebbs)
2. 安装 Graphviz (https://graphviz.org/download/)
3. 配置 `settings.json`:
```json
{
  "plantuml.graphviz": "C:\\Program Files\\Graphviz\\bin\\dot.exe",
  "plantuml.jar": "C:\\plantuml\\plantuml.jar"
}
```

### 导出命令
```bash
# 导出 PNG
java -jar plantuml.jar -tpng uml.md

# 导出 SVG
java -jar plantuml.jar -tsvg uml.md

# 导出 PDF
java -jar plantuml.jar -tpdf uml.md
```

### 配置主题
```plantuml
!theme plain
!theme bluegray
!theme mint
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4.puml
```

